583
00:25:17,000 --> 00:25:19,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ja vas nikad neću ostaviti.

584
00:25:19,000 --> 00:25:20,000
[SPEAKER_00] Vi ste moji.

585
00:25:20,000 --> 00:25:26,000
[SPEAKER_00] Dječice, ja čekam svoje moje djecu, navratim od nebeskih, daj zagrlim i dobrodošim.

586
00:25:26,000 --> 00:25:29,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ja vas ljubim takvi kakvi jeste.

587
00:25:29,000 --> 00:25:31,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ljubim vas neizmjenom ljubavlju.

588
00:25:31,000 --> 00:25:36,000
