593
00:25:43,000 --> 00:25:45,000
[SPEAKER_00] Kako?

594
00:25:45,000 --> 00:25:47,000
[SPEAKER_00] Eto, majka je majka.

595
00:25:47,000 --> 00:25:52,000
[SPEAKER_00] I govori, dječice, ako živite moje poruke vidjet ćete čudesa.

