[SPEAKER_00] I ona kaže, dječice, ako mi date vaše srce, ja ću ga promijeniti učiniti kao moje.

600
00:26:05,000 --> 00:26:10,000
[SPEAKER_00] Njezino srce koje je ljubilo onih koji su razapili njezinog sina.

601
00:26:10,000 --> 00:26:13,000
[SPEAKER_00] S istom ljubavlju s kojom je ljubila svoga sina.

602
00:26:13,000 --> 00:26:17,000
[SPEAKER_00] Evo srce koje možemo primiti kad primimo nju.

603
00:26:17,000 --> 00:26:19,000
[SPEAKER_00] Kad molimo nju za njezino srce.

604
00:26:19,000 --> 00:26:22,000
[SPEAKER_00] Evo srce koje treba cijeli svijet.

605
00:26:22,000 --> 00:26:25,000
[SPEAKER_00] Naši prijatelji, neprijatelji, rodbina.

606
00:26:25,000 --> 00:26:29,000
[SPEAKER_00] A ovo stvari nema ko nije naša rodbina.

607
00:26:29,000 --> 00:26:34,000
[SPEAKER_00] Kako me duboko potaknula ona poruka koja je dala Mirjani drugoga.

608
00:26:34,000 --> 00:26:36,000
[SPEAKER_00] U mjesecu kad je rekla:

609
00:26:36,000 --> 00:26:40,000
[SPEAKER_00] Moj sin kad je bio maleni, pričao bi mi.

610
00:26:40,000 --> 00:26:42,000
[SPEAKER_00] Govorio bi mi.

611
00:26:42,000 --> 00:26:46,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da su svi ljudi njegova braća.

612
00:26:46,000 --> 00:26:50,000
[SPEAKER_00] Svi ljudi.

613
00:26:50,000 --> 00:26:52,000
[SPEAKER_00] Svi smo jedno.

614
00:26:52,000 --> 00:26:54,000
[SPEAKER_00] Svi.

615
00:26:54,000 --> 00:26:56,000
[SPEAKER_00] I Gospa kaže:

616
00:26:56,000 --> 00:27:00,000
[SPEAKER_00] Molim vas, nemojte dopustiti da moje srce plaće krvave suze.

617
00:27:00,000 --> 00:27:02,000
[SPEAKER_00] Zbog griješnika koji se gube u grijehu.

618
00:27:02,000 --> 00:27:06,000
[SPEAKER_00] Koliko to veličanstveno.

619
00:27:06,000 --> 00:27:08,000
[SPEAKER_00] Koliko nas to uči.

620
00:27:08,000 --> 00:27:12,000
[SPEAKER_00] Kako je to srce koje želimo da bude naše srce.

621
00:27:12,000 --> 00:27:16,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ona ne plaće za to što je ona ranjena.

622
00:27:16,000 --> 00:27:20,000
[SPEAKER_00] Što se protiv nje i njeznog sina okreću što je sin ranjen.

623
00:27:20,000 --> 00:27:22,000
[SPEAKER_00] nego što se gube duše.

624
00:27:22,000 --> 00:27:24,000
[SPEAKER_00] I ona kaže:

625
00:27:24,000 --> 00:27:26,000
[SPEAKER_00] Dječice,

626
00:27:26,000 --> 00:27:30,000
[SPEAKER_00] Vaš zivot na zemlji trepej oka na spremježnosti.

627
00:27:30,000 --> 00:27:32,000
[SPEAKER_00] Trepej oka.

628
00:27:32,000 --> 00:27:36,000
[SPEAKER_00] Eto zašto je toliko važno vaša zajednica koja se bori.

629
00:27:36,000 --> 00:27:40,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da uskrsli Isus bude u stredini.

630
00:27:40,000 --> 00:27:42,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da ga se hrabro slijedi naprijed.

631
00:27:42,000 --> 00:27:48,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da obitelji, pojedinci i svećenici i posvećeni

632
00:27:48,000 --> 00:27:50,000
[SPEAKER_00] Mogu imati tu hrabrost.

633
00:27:50,000 --> 00:27:52,000
[SPEAKER_00] Zajedništva.

634
00:27:52,000 --> 00:27:54,000
[SPEAKER_00] Zajedno koracati prema nebu.

635
00:27:54,000 --> 00:27:56,000
[SPEAKER_00] I Gospod nam govori:

636
00:27:56,000 --> 00:27:58,000
[SPEAKER_00] Dječice,

637
00:27:58,000 --> 00:28:00,000
[SPEAKER_00] Budite vi

638
00:28:00,000 --> 00:28:02,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ljepota.

639
00:28:02,000 --> 00:28:04,000
[SPEAKER_00] Budite vi

640
00:28:04,000 --> 00:28:05,000
[SPEAKER_00] Radost.

641
00:28:05,000 --> 00:28:06,000
[SPEAKER_00] Budite vi

642
00:28:06,000 --> 00:28:07,000
[SPEAKER_00] Mir.

643
00:28:07,000 --> 00:28:08,000
[SPEAKER_00] Budite vi

644
00:28:08,000 --> 00:28:09,000
[SPEAKER_00] Nada.

645
00:28:09,000 --> 00:28:15,000
[SPEAKER_00] A napose budite molitvo za sve one koji ne poznaju ljubav Božju i ljubav moju.

646
00:28:15,000 --> 00:28:17,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ponovo.

647
00:28:17,000 --> 00:28:19,000
[SPEAKER_00] Kako?

648
00:28:19,000 --> 00:28:21,000
[SPEAKER_00] Korak po korak.

649
00:28:21,000 --> 00:28:23,000
[SPEAKER_00] Malo pa malo.

650
00:28:23,000 --> 00:28:25,000
[SPEAKER_00] Živiti tih pet koraka.

651
00:28:25,000 --> 00:28:29,000
[SPEAKER_00] Kao što pravi Jozovi bi rekao pet kamenčića Gospine.

652
00:28:29,000 --> 00:28:31,000
[SPEAKER_00] Goli protiv Golijata.

653
00:28:31,000 --> 00:28:33,000
[SPEAKER_00] Davidovi kamenčića protiv Golijata.

654
00:28:33,000 --> 00:28:35,000
[SPEAKER_00] A svaki imamo naša Golijata.

655
00:28:35,000 --> 00:28:39,000
[SPEAKER_00] A najviše onoga koji živi u namu.

656
00:28:39,000 --> 00:28:41,000
[SPEAKER_00] Koji prkosi ne da se...

657
00:28:41,000 --> 00:28:42,000
[SPEAKER_00] Zove se Ego.

658
00:28:42,000 --> 00:28:43,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ja.

659
00:28:43,000 --> 00:28:45,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ne ti nego ja.

660
00:28:45,000 --> 00:28:48,000
[SPEAKER_00] I zato ovdje imamo taj veliki dar.

661
00:28:48,000 --> 00:28:51,000
[SPEAKER_00] Tisuće i tisuće ljudi koji dolaze.

662
00:28:51,000 --> 00:28:55,000
[SPEAKER_00] Evo baš u posljednjih tri godina prije Covid-a.

663
00:28:55,000 --> 00:29:00,000
[SPEAKER_00] Imali smo više od 65 tisuća odrčanstvenika svakog godina koji su došli na svjedočanstvo ovdje.

664
00:29:00,000 --> 00:29:03,000
[SPEAKER_00] iz cijeli svih dijelova svijeta.

665
00:29:03,000 --> 00:29:08,000
[SPEAKER_00] Za seminar za svećnike imali mi 150 svećnika, baš u ovoj sali.

666
00:29:08,000 --> 00:29:10,000
[SPEAKER_00] 150 svećnika bogoslava.

667
00:29:10,000 --> 00:29:13,000
[SPEAKER_00] Najviše iz Ukrajine.

668
00:29:13,000 --> 00:29:17,000
[SPEAKER_00] Na duhovnim obrnovama što drže se ovdje u župi.

669
00:29:17,000 --> 00:29:20,000
[SPEAKER_00] Sad imamo četvero, momentalno.

670
00:29:20,000 --> 00:29:23,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ali svi su u našem srcu sada.

671
00:29:23,000 --> 00:29:25,000
[SPEAKER_00] Oni nisu odsudni.

672
00:29:25,000 --> 00:29:32,000
[SPEAKER_00] I mi vidimo te velike, velike darove što gospodin daruje.

673
00:29:32,000 --> 00:29:34,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ne vidimo gospu.

674
00:29:34,000 --> 00:29:38,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ovdje se je ukazala mnogo puta, čak i na ovom mjestu ovdje.

675
00:29:38,000 --> 00:29:40,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ali tada isto nismo ime vidjeli.

676
00:29:40,000 --> 00:29:43,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ali znamo da je tu.

